{
  "stem": "935.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that is when a guy from outside said, hey, general, or whatever, look.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This is open.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The whole thing is open here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They tried to crawl out from here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And, you know, Jews always lie, and they should be shot just for lying, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Let me show you, let me show you the boards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They didn't-- it won't-- it was like a coffin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Where they couldn't cut-- shut it enough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So half of it was gone in the wind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when I moved away from it, this was going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And one guy from those easy beavers saw that, and wanted the guy to come and look that there was-- we had cut out a board.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He didn't want to have anything to do with it anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they went on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But what happened is, just as I sat down, there was a knife coming through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "This guy, who said, the board is open-- he had put his knife through to see that it was open.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So where I had stood just few seconds ago, there was this knife coming through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I was sitting on the floor and I thought then, well, it means that there's still a chance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Even though I wouldn't have known what.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I didn't know there was a knife until much later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "As the train started to go again, the other people in the car said, of course, you got to throw all these things out-- the hammer and saw.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It's no good anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It will only cause us problems, because they're going to stop the train again and again and again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Didn't want to do it, they didn't want to do it yet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We thought, perhaps somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
